{
  "stem": "20978.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course, I didn't know how to talk to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And until I got to know it, I got whipped a few times because I got out of line.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The cows moved, you know, went the wrong way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I messed up the, the plowing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I learned that, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the Ukrainian guard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And they called you the dirty Jew and-- besides a few chosen words.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This, this was an estate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was a, a huge farm that belonged to an Austrian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] His-- he, he lived there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His family lived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was-- you know, the houses itself was the perimeter, the fence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a huge gate-- and the stables.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In other words, it was like a circle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there were barracks, you know, where, where they put-- built bunks where we stayed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About 10.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I was with my mother and two sisters and some other people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had bunk beds, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] you know, with straw, hay.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Debrecen?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but I got to know the people that we were-- were there, that we worked with.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't remember their names anymore.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't even know how many they-- how many survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because when-- after, they-- when they took us from that farm, a lot of them died out at the front lines, like, like my mother.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they, they were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were shot by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The front lines was between the Germans and the Russians, where they were fighting The Russians were--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the Germans-- they tried to take us, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we ran away.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
